“Njengamanje kunzima ezibhedlela ukuthi zibhekana nomthamo wabantu abaguliswa yileli gciwane. Kube kakhulu ezibhedlela zikahulumeni njengoba amagumbi abo abagula kakhulu egcwele phama, basebenza kanzima ukuqinisekisa ukuthi wonke umuntu ogula kakhulu uyakuthola ukunakekeleka , sekusiza nezibhedlela ezizimela,"usho kanje. Uthe nokho kwezinye izifuundazwe isimo asizoba sibi kakhulu. “I-Eastern Cape, ibonakala iza kabi kakhulu njengoba yona kulindeleke ukuthi iphelelwe yimibhede maphakathi noJune kodwa kuzoba kubi kakhulu ngoJulayi. IGauteng yona ingalandela ngesinye isikhathi neFree State.” 